'''Omnicide''' is a term used to describe the destruction of species through [[nuclear war]]. It may also be used as a general term for [[industrial pollution]].  The prefix ''omni'' also means all, so in this case, omnicide is the death of all things.

Omnicide truly means to kill everything, this can be achieved through several means.  A supporter of omnicide generally hates everything, thus wanting everything to die.

The greenhouse effect could in return cause an omnicide to different species, such as polar bears